										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<span class="span-reading-time rt-reading-time" style="display: block;"><span class="rt-label rt-prefix">Reading Time: </span> <span class="rt-time"> 3</span> <span class="rt-label rt-postfix">minutes</span></span>
<p>Teddi Mellencamp shared that her dad, John Mellencamp, already has a plan to lay her to rest.</p>



<p>Amidst her battle with <a href="https://www.thehollywoodgossip.com/2025/04/teddi-mellencamp-reveals-stage-4-cancer-diagnosis/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">stage 4 cancer</a>, which includes numerous tumors in <a href="https://www.thehollywoodgossip.com/2025/03/teddi-mellencamp-says-new-tumors-were-found-in-her-brain-lungs-i-will-beat-these/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">her brain and lungs</a>, she is drawing up a will.</p>



<p>Her famous father has been anxious to cement her burial plans with her.</p>



<p>The <em>RHOBH </em>alum had to have a heavy conversation &#8212; and she knows that it&#8217;s about more than her and her father.</p>


