<p>In a moment of levity, Teddi joked that she would like to have the quote, &#8220;Hot girls never die,&#8221; engraved upon her tombstone.</p>



<p>(That quote became the title of that podcast episode)</p>



<p>Teddi presumably does not intend for her ex to be part of the mausoleum. </p>



<p>Though she shares her three children with Edwin Arroyave, the two split just six months ago, in October 2024 &#8212; following 14 years of marriage.</p>


